00:00:02.420 --> 00:00:04.260
Welcome to Instant Cooking

00:00:04.560 --> 00:00:07.080
Today I am making Stuffed Chilli Pickle

00:00:07.280 --> 00:00:09.980
For this we need Dry mango powder

00:00:10.720 --> 00:00:13.960
Turmeric powder, Salt to taste, Black Salt

00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:16.700
Red Chilli powder, Onion Seed

00:00:17.960 --> 00:00:20.640
Fennel Seed, Coriander Seed

00:00:22.840 --> 00:00:25.300
Fenugreek Seed, Cumin Seed

00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:29.420
And mustard seeds or mustard pulse &amp; mustard seed oil

00:00:29.460 --> 00:00:30.580
take a frying pan

00:00:31.380 --> 00:00:34.580
On very low flame add 4 tsp of fennel seeds

00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:41.880
Toss it up add 3 tsp of coriander seed

00:00:46.020 --> 00:00:49.720
and 1-1/2 tsp of fenugreek seed

00:00:49.720 --> 00:00:55.580
Mix it and cook it for couple of seconds, now add 1 tsp of cumin seed

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.620
1 tsp of onion seed mix it

00:01:00.720 --> 00:01:05.700
and cook it for 1/2 minute then put it into a grinder

00:01:05.860 --> 00:01:07.300
and coarsely grind it

00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:14.140
Now add a pinch of black salt and coarsely grind it again

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:17.120
now take a frying pan

00:01:17.580 --> 00:01:20.280
Add 8 tbsp of mustard seed oil

00:01:20.780 --> 00:01:24.180
Add 1/2 tsp of asafoetida

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:29.600
1/2 tsp of turmeric powder, 1/2 tsp of red chilly powder or as per your taste

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:32.360
Now add our coarsely grind masala

00:01:33.060 --> 00:01:39.600
Mix it again and then add 8-10 tsp of mustard pulse or mustard seeds

00:01:41.780 --> 00:01:45.640
mix it well add salt to taste

00:01:50.620 --> 00:01:53.640
Add 1/2 tsp of Dry mango powder

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:58.880
Mix all the ingredients

00:02:02.340 --> 00:02:08.460
Now slit the green chilly and make the space for stuffing using the spoon

00:02:08.980 --> 00:02:10.200
Stuff the masala

00:02:11.620 --> 00:02:13.000
Stuff completely

00:02:22.380 --> 00:02:26.040
Put it into a pickle container

00:02:31.980 --> 00:02:35.160
Put rest of masala on top of chilly

00:02:35.720 --> 00:02:37.380
Add pinch of salt

00:02:37.880 --> 00:02:40.600
and 3-4 spoon of mustard seed oil

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:43.400
Your Stuffed Chilli Pickle is ready. Thank you...

